cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on the design of a graphical user interface for a social robot that assists people with developmental disabilities. This involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybernetics (cs.CY), and social and information systems (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC, followed by cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CY, and cs.SI.
